   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <funcsynopsis>
     <funcdef>int <function>mcrypt_get_key_size</function></funcdef>
     <paramdef>int <parameter>cipher</parameter></paramdef>
    </funcsynopsis>
	
    <para>
     <function>mcrypt_get_key_size</function> is used to get the size of a key
